data.meta_description: We manage Holmen’s forests, procure wood for Holmen’s Swedish sawmills, paper and paperboard mills. And we purchase and sell wood from private forest owners, forest owner associations and sawmills.
data.text:
Holmen endeavors to ensure having as good a picture as possible of the origin of the wood. We have the following requirements when purchasingwood. Holmen only buys wood from Natura 2000 sites if the seller can present a valid felling application and necessary permits.
